<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of the second paragraph of Article 15 of the Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The examination of pesticide residues shall include the pesticide itself and its metabolites. Both the MRLs (ppm) and the actually detected residues of pesticides are calculated on the basis of the weights of the products sold on the market.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The pesticide residue limits in animal products shall meet the following Table. Not listed in the Table shall not be detected.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard shall be implemented from the date of promulgation.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
